History

  I can trace Objex back to some of the earliest work I did in IT. I've kind of started
  Objex a number of times on a number of different platforms and languages, but never
  really finished it. It has become, therefore, kind of a pet project that I've had
  on the go for some time and I have used it to keep myself relatively up to date as
  my day-job doesn't allow me to do much coding anymore :(.

